<plot>Renewalis the first feature-length documentary to capture the vitality of America's religious-environmental movement. Offering a profound message of hope, in eight stories, Renewal shows people inspired by their diverse spiritual and religious convictions, being called to re-examine what it means to be human and how we live on this planet.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?460287</url></doc>
